title: Standup comedy - The sorta complete Patton Oswalt
description: Officially, Patton Oswalt has put out 2 formal comedy albums and has had a couple of standup specials on HBO and Comedy Central. There are also a few bootlegs of concerts going around, and the only way to get them is to power up the old P2P napsterclones and hope for the best. In this torrent are both full albums, rips from the specials, and as much of the various bootleg stuff as I could find. If anyone has anything I am missing, please upload it and link to me here.
